articles.title: Why are major car-sharing firms not stepping into the point-to-point void amid BlueSG's pause?
articles.content: The company is the only car-sharing platform that offers point-to-point services in Singapore. Experts said its move to suspend operations was likely influenced by losses caused by an ageing fleet.
